 href=\"https://youtu.be/yW35eEhJOG0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyW35eEhJOG0&d=JKgkomYAlrGnBBGbQ5QdW6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d49dc5ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yW35eEhJOG0</a></blockquote><br />\n隻蟲出左黎佢就死左？ 隻蟲係佢本體？</blockquote><br />\n寄生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6330c6b424b8c97319378acf8687a598221173","tid":289123,"uid":67848,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T22:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/yW35eEhJOG0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyW35eEhJOG0&d=JKgkomYAlrGnBBGbQ5QdW6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d49dc5ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yW35eEhJOG0</a></blockquote><br />\n隻蟲出左黎佢就死左？ 隻蟲係佢本體？</blockquote><br />\n隻蟲係寄生蟲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢種係寄生蟲係喺水中產卵繁殖 所以中咗寄生蟲嘅螳螂會自己走去水到(正常唔屬水性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n最終因此而浸死自己 而寄生蟲就藉此走出嚟繁殖<br />\n(希望無記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n所以我諗叫人拎去水刑嘅巴打只係想睇有無寄生蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b23ec3b69954d77e0385b5c5b41e3a3950d3d7","tid":289123,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T22:21:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/yW35eEhJOG0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyW35eEhJOG0&d=JKgkomYAlrGnBBGbQ5QdW6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d49dc5ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yW35eEhJOG0</a></blockquote><br />\n隻蟲出左黎佢就死左？ 隻蟲係佢本體？</blockquote><br />\n隻蟲係寄生蟲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢種係寄生蟲係喺水中產卵繁殖 所以中咗寄生蟲嘅螳螂會自己走去水到(正常唔屬水性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n最終因此而浸死自己 而寄生蟲就藉此走出嚟繁殖<br />\n(希望無記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa